Text: Thank Youyou for stopping by the Boardroom yesterday to congratulate me on my college graduation It is due to Enron that I have been able to achieve this lifelong goal I have also received unfailing encouragement support and flexibility from Cliff during this time Had it not been for Cliff I would not have been nearly so successful My deepest thanks to the three of you
